lding%20Swipecast%2C%20a%20career%20platform%20for%20creative%20professionals%2C%20and%20Wickenburg%20was%20working%20on%20competitor%20Mixer.%20But%20they%20bonded%20over%20a%20shared%20pain%20point%3A%20sales%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20calls%20were%20a%20nuisance%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20hard%20to%20know%20what%20was%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Bennaceur%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20nothing%20to%20record%20calls%20or%20transcribe%20the%20conversation%2C%20so%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20volume%20out%20of%20these%20conversations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20they%20forged%20an%20alliance%20and%2C%20in%202021%2C%20launched%20Attention%20to%20help%20solve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20spent%20eight%20months%20working%20on%20the%20first%20iteration%20of%20Attention%2C%20which%20used%20AI%20to%20coach%20sales%20reps.%20When%20that%20version%20struggled%20to%20find%20product-market%20fit%2C%20they%20pivoted%20in%20mid-2022%20to%20develop%20a%20program%20that%20used%20AI%20to%20transcribe%20sales%20calls%20and%20automatically%20fill%20out%20the%20CRM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Swipecast%20was%20bootstrapped%20during%20its%20six-year%20run%2C%20Bennaceur%20and%20Wickenburg%20knew%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20go%20the%20VC%20route%20with%20Attention%20to%20match%20deeper%20competition%20in%20the%20enterprise%20tech%20space%20and%20hire%20enough%20engineering%20talent%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttention's%20AI%20analyzes%20sales%20team%20calls%20and%20generates%20action%20items%20such%20as%20follow-up%20emails%20and%20Salesforce%20updates.%20The%20tech%20can%20also%20identify%20customers%20who%20are%20a%20churn%20risk%20and%20provide%20scorecards.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20new%20round%20of%20funding%2C%20Attention%20will%20focus%20on%20automating%20more%20business%20tasks%20with%20the%20broader%20vision%20of%20%26quot%3Bputting%20the%20sales%20team%20on%20autopilot%2C%26quot%3B%20Bennaceur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20filling%20out%20a%20CRM%2C%20he%20envisions%20a%20world%20where%20his%20tech%20prepares%20handover%20notes%2C%20mitigates%20churn%20risks%2C%20handles%20email%20correspondence%20and%20customer%20tickets%2C%20and%20analyzes%20the%20data%20provided%20by%20customer%20interactions%20through%20the%20sales%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20building%20an%20engine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20companies%20to%20have%20as%20lean%20of%20a%20team%20as%20possible%20that%20generates%20100x%20of%20the%20outputs%20that%20you%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttention%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20companies%20in%20the%20growing%20business%20of%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20improve%20sales%20and%20supercharge%20the%20enterprise%20software%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate-stage%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gong.io%2Fpress%2Fgong-raises-250-million-in-series-e-funding-at-7-25-billion-valuation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGong%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20records%20sales%20calls%2C%20raised%20%24250%20million%20in%20Series%20E%20funding%20in%202021%20at%20a%20%247.25%20billion%20valuation.%20And%2011x.ai%2C%20which%20is%20building%20AI%20sales%20reps%2C%20raised%20a%20%2450%20million%20Series%20B%20last%20month%20from%20a16z%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F09%2F30%2F11x-ai-a-developer-of-ai-sales-reps-has-raised-50m-series-b-led-by-a16z-sources-say%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattention-series-a-analyze-sales-calls-ai-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729602001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6716767f9b3250dbbce8b929%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattention-series-a-analyze-sales-calls-ai-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attention%20uses%20AI%20and%20natural%20language%20processing%20to%20record%20sales%20calls%2C%20analyze%20data%2C%20and%20generate%20next%20steps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sstokes%40insider.com%20(Samantha%20Stokes)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattention-series-a-analyze-sales-calls-ai-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20BRICS%2B%20Wants%20To%20Reshape%20US-Led%20Economic%20Order.%20It%20Won't%20Be%20Easy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fhifkia7o_brics_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%2015%20years%20since%20its%20first%20summit.%20Back%20then.%20BRICS%20was%20BRIC.%20And%20now%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20BRICS%20but%20BRICS%2B.%20The%20summit%20in%20Kazan%20is%20seeing%20the%20member%20nations%20go%20up%20from%20five%20to%20nine%2C%20with%20one%20more%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20having%20been%20invited%20to%20join.%20According%20to%20Russian%20foreign%20minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%2C%20there%20are%2030%20more%20countries%20that%20have%20been%20in%20touch%20over%20joining%20the%20BRICS%2B%20in%20some%20format%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Goldman%20Sach's%20economist%20Jim%20O'Neill%20coined%20the%20acronym%20BRIC%20and%20predicted%20that%20the%20economies%20of%20the%20four%20member%20countries%20-%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20and%20China%20-%20would%20dominate%20the%20global%20economy%20by%202050%2C%20his%20projection%20was%20based%20only%20on%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20four%20nations.%20The%20grouping%20now%20represents%20a%20combined%20GDP%20that%20exceeds%20the%20G7's%20by%20%26quot%3Babout%205%20percentage%20points%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Summit.%20A%20briefing%20note%20of%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20titled%20%3Cem%3EExpansion%20of%20BRICS%3A%20A%20Quest%20for%20Greater%20Global%20Influence%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20says%20that%20BRICS%2B%20accounts%20for%2037.3%25%20of%20the%20world's%20GDP.%20That%20is%20more%20than%20half%20as%20much%20as%20the%20European%20Union's%2014.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BArtificial%20Efforts%20To%20Maintain%20Dollar's%20Position%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavrov%20also%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20US-led%20world%20order%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20unwilling%20to%20relinquish%20the%20reins%20of%20power%20that%20they%20have%20held%20since%20World%20War%20II%20through%20the%20Bretton%20Woods%20institutions%20and%20through%20the%20role%20assigned%20to%20the%20US%20dollar%20in%20the%20international%20monetary%20system%2C%20even%20after%20the%20free%20exchange%20of%20US%20dollars%20for%20gold%20had%20been%20cancelled.%20The%20leading%20position%20of%20this%20currency%20is%20maintained%20by%20efforts%20that%20are%20largely%20artificial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRICS%2B%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20taking%20the%20first%20step%20to%20break%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20dollar%2C%20by%20a%20proposed%20launch%20of%20an%20international%20payment%20system%20that%20can%20circumvent%20the%20dollar.%20India's%20foreign%20secretary%2C%20Vikram%20Misri%2C%20confirmed%20that%20there%20had%20been%20discussions%20that%20had%20been%20underway%20on%20settlement%20systems%20and%20payment%20systems.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20as%20per%20his%20understanding%2C%20no%20final%20agreements%20have%20been%20arrived%20at%20yet.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20fundamentally%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20countries%20have%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20use%20of%20local%20currencies%20for%20settlement%20purposes%20especially%20as%20it%20comes%20to%20or%20as%20it%20pertains%20to%20trade.%20So%2C%20strengthening%20of%20correspondent%20banking%20networks%20amongst%20the%20BRICS%20partners%20and%20enabling%20settlements%20in%20local%20currencies%20is%20being%20encouraged%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Threat%20Of%20Sanctions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Western%20sanctions%20faced%20by%20Russia%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Moscow%20is%20most%20keen%20to%20push%20the%20idea%20through%20not%20just%20to%20break%20the%20dollar's%20dominance%20but%20also%20to%20showcase%20to%20the%20West%20that%20it%20still%20has%20allies%20and%20partners%20on%20its%20side.%20Iran%2C%20the%20new%20BRICS%2B%20member%2C%20also%20faces%20crippling%20US%20sanctions%20and%20Moscow%20hopes%20for%20support%20from%20the%20members%20that%20have%20increasingly%20felt%20that%20the%20West-dominated%20economic%20order%20has%20short-changed%20the%20rest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Summit%2C%20Russian%20Finance%20Minister%20Anton%20Siluanov%20also%20called%20for%20new%20institutions%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Bretton%20Woods%20institutions%2C%20saying%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20and%20the%20World%20Bank%20are%20not%20performing%20their%20roles.%20However%2C%20the%20big%20question%20is%20whether%20a%20member%20country%20like%20China%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20current%20global%20world%20order%2C%20will%20seek%20a%20new%20parallel%20system%20altogether%20when%20it%20is%20pushing%20for%20reforms%20along%20with%20countries%20like%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReforming%20The%20IMF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20IMF%20publication%20by%20India's%20former%20Governor%20of%20the%20Central%20Bank%2C%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20sought%20not%20just%20quota%20reforms%20in%20IMF%20but%20also%20a%20change%20in%20the%20body's%20governance%20to%20make%20it%20both%20fair%20and%20more%20representative%20of%20the%20current%20global%20realities.%20He%20said%20if%20members%20reform%20quotas%20and%20governance%20simultaneously%2C%20an%20independent%20IMF%20could%20bring%20a%20fragmenting%20world%20together%20on%20key%20issues.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20comprehensive%20reforms%20should%20happen%20soon%3B%20else%20the%20rest%20could%20well%20believe%20this%20is%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Western%20alliance%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20some%20influence%20just%20when%20power%20is%20finally%20shifting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BRICS%2B%20also%20has%20its%20task%20cut%20out.%20Much%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20outcome%20too.%20For%20example%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20said%20that%20he%20will%20penalise%20countries%20that%20move%20away%20from%20the%20dollar%20by%20imposing%20a%20100%25%20tariff%20on%20their%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMF%2C%20the%20dollar%20remains%20a%20dominant%20force%2C%20with%2059%25%20of%20official%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20and%20the%20euro%20second%20at%20approximately%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20the%20speculation%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20keenly%20trained%20on%20Russia%20for%20any%20indication%20in%20this%20direction%20during%20the%20two-day%20event.%20The%20announcement%2C%20if%20any%2C%20will%20have%20even%20greater%20significance%20because%20it%20will%20come%20from%20a%20country%20that%20is%20at%20direct%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20Western%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Maha%20Siddiqui%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20extensively%20reported%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20global%20affairs.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729602000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h