e%22%3A%22CWG%20Decision%20To%20Drop%20Badminton%2C%20Hockey%20Aimed%20To%20'Stunt'%20India%3A%20Gopichand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20legendary%20Pullela%20Gopichand%20and%20Vimal%20Kumar%20on%20Tuesday%20slammed%20the%20decision%20to%20exclude%20sports%20such%20as%20badminton%20from%202026%20Glasgow%20Commonwealth%20Games%20and%20urged%20the%20country%20to%20not%20send%20a%20team%20to%20the%20event%20as%20it%20is%20aimed%20at%20%26quot%3Bstunting%26quot%3B%20India's%20progress.%20In%20a%20blow%20to%20India's%20medal%20prospects%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20key%20sports%20such%20as%20hockey%2C%20badminton%2C%20wrestling%2C%20cricket%2C%20table%20tennis%20and%20shooting%20have%20been%20dropped%20from%20the%202026%20edition%20by%20host%20city%20Glasgow%2C%20which%20unveiled%20a%20pruned%20roster%20of%2010%20disciplines%20to%20keep%20the%20event%20budget-friendly%20and%20free%20of%20%26quot%3Boperational%20risks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20roster%20has%20stunned%20the%20Indian%20sports%20fraternity%20with%20Gopichand%20and%20Vimal%20coming%20out%20with%20the%20strongest%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20need%20for%20CWG.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20they%20should%20do%20away%20with%20it.%20It%20is%20better%20to%20organise%20Olympics%20and%20Asian%20Games%20than%20CWG.%20It%20is%20pathetic%2C%20I%20am%20really%20disappointed.%20CWG%20is%20losing%20its%20charm%2C%20it's%20relevance%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20strongly%20we%20shouldn't%20send%20out%20a%20team%20for%20CWG%2C%20it%20is%20not%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20India%20coach%20Vimal%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20CWG%20it%20is%20important%20to%20look%20at%20ways%20to%20provide%20better%20facilities%20to%20athletes%20at%20Olympics%20and%20Asian%20Games.%20CWG%20is%20not%20required.%20You%20have%20to%20put%20good%20physical%20sport%20in%20the%20program%2C%20if%20you%20take%20away%20all%20that%20then%20what's%20the%20point%2C%26quot%3