ance%20on%20August%2028%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20investigation%20that%20unearthed%20betrayal%2C%20deceit%2C%20and%20a%20horrifying%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20case%20bears%20a%20resemblance%20to%20the%20movie%20Drishyam%20where%20the%20accused%20meticulously%20planned%20and%20executed%20the%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prima%20facie%20motive%20behind%20the%20crime%20is%20the%20romantic%20relationship%20turning%20sour%20due%20to%20opposition%20by%20the%20accused's%20family%20to%20their%20marriage%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20individual%2C%20identified%20as%20Ajay%20Wankhede%20(33)%2C%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Kailash%20Nagar%20area%20in%20Nagpur%20and%20is%20stationed%20in%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20investigators%2C%20Wankhede%20had%20met%20Jyotsna%20Aakre%2C%20a%20divorcee%2C%20through%20a%20marriage%20portal%20and%20their%20friendship%20soon%20blossomed%20into%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20things%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20worse%20after%20Wankhede's%20family%20opposed%20their%20union%20and%20married%20him%20off%20with%20another%20woman%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWankhede%20subsequently%20started%20ignoring%20Aakre.%20He%20might%20have%20planned%20the%20murder%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20her%2C%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWankhede%20is%20accused%20of%20administering%20a%20sedative%20to%20Aakre%2C%20strangling%20her%20to%20death%2C%20and%20then%20burying%20her%20body%20in%20a%20secluded%20location%20in%20Nagpur%20district.%20He%20even%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20covering%20the%20body%20with%20cement%20to%20conceal%20the%20crime%2C%20the%20official%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Wankhede%20stopped%20answering%20Aakre's%20phone%20calls%2C%20she%20began%20searching%20for%20him%20and%20managed%20to%20contact%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20his%2C%20who%20disclosed%20his%20(Wankhede's)%20whereabouts.%20The%20friend%20also%20conveyed%20to%20Wankhede%20that%20Aakre%20was%20looking%20for%20him%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlarmed%20by%20the%20situation%2C%20Wankhede%20called%20Aakre%20using%20his%20mother's%20mobile%20phone%20and%20invited%20her%20to%20meet%20on%20Wardha%20Road%20on%20August%2028%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakre%20informed%20her%20family%20that%20she%20was%20staying%20with%20a%20friend%20that%20day%20and%20would%20return%20home%20after%20finishing%20her%20duties%20the%20next%20day.%20She%20was%20employed%20with%20an%20automobile%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWankhede%20and%20Aakre%20met%20in%20the%20Wardha%20Road%20area%20and%20checked%20into%20a%20hotel.%20Later%2C%20they%20left%20the%20hotel%20and%20drove%20to%20a%20nearby%20toll%20plaza%2C%20where%20he%20offered%20her%20a%20drink%20laced%20with%20a%20sedative%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Aakre%20fell%20unconscious%2C%20Wankhede%20strangled%20her%20to%20death%20and%20drove%20to%20a%20secluded%20area%2C%20where%20he%20dug%20a%20pit%20at%20night%2C%20dumped%20her%20body%2C%20and%20covered%20it%20with%20cement.%20Later%2C%20he%20threw%20the%20mobile%20phone%20of%20Aakre%20in%20a%20truck%20passing%20through%20Wardha%20road%2C%20according%20to%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aakre%20didn't%20return%20home%2C%20her%20family%20reported%20her%20missing%20to%20the%20Beltarodi%20police%20on%20August%2029.%20An%20investigation%20was%20launched%2C%20and%20a%20case%20of%20kidnapping%20was%20registered%20on%20September%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20police%20checked%20the%20call%20detail%20records%20and%20found%20regular%20phone%20calls%20between%20Wankhede%20and%20Aakre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20summoned%20Wankhede%20for%20questioning.%20Sensing%20trouble%2C%20he%20sought%20medical%20attention%20for%20high%20blood%20pressure%20at%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Medical%20College%20in%20Pune%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Wankhede%20applied%20for%20anticipatory%20bail%20in%20the%20sessions%20court%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20but%20his%20plea%20was%20rejected.%20He%20then%20approached%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20also%20denied%20his%20application%20on%20September%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20rejection%20of%20his%20anticipatory%20bail%2C%20the%20Beltarodi%20police%20arrested%20Wankhede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20Wankhede%20disclosed%20the%20location%20of%20the%20crime%20scene.%20Police%20went%20to%20the%20site%20with%20forensic%20experts%20and%20exhumed%20the%20body%20parts%20on%20Monday%20near%20Dongargaon%20toll%20plaza%20on%20Wardha%20road%20in%20Nagpur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729600560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2F204ao7pg_maharashtra-police_625x300_12_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-soldier-arrested-for-drishyam-style-murder-of-girlfriend-in-nagpur-6847753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Army%20jawan%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20Nagpur%20Police%20for%20allegedly%20killing%20his%20girlfriend%20and%20covering%20her%20body%20with%20cement%20after%20burying%20her%2C%20a%20chilling%20crime%20that%20mirrors%20a%20plot%20from%20the%20film%20Drishyam%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Kamala%20Harris%20eating%20marijuana%20gummies%20to%20relax%20during%20election%20season%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729600486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-11446597