0firm%20has%20reassessed%20its%20tech%20stack%20as%20it%20eyes%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECTO%20Josh%20Woods%20and%20COO%20of%20technology%20Jeff%20Maurone%20discuss%20how%20the%20firm%20is%20rebuilding%20for%20its%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Citadel%20Securities%20COO%20of%20technology%2C%20Jeff%20Maurone%2C%20was%20meeting%20with%20senior%20leaders%20to%20discuss%20technology%20priorities%20for%20the%20year.%20But%20what%20started%20as%20a%20standard%20strategy%20meeting%20resulted%20in%20a%20yearslong%20re-evaluation%20and%20rebuild%20across%20the%20market%20maker's%20entire%20technology%20stack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaurone%20said%20the%20meeting%20was%20a%20rallying%20cry%20for%20simplicity%20and%20walked%20away%20with%20an%20assignment%20he%20positioned%20like%20this%3A%20%26quot%3BImagine%20if%20you%20were%20an%20airline%2C%20could%20you%2C%20on%20one%20PowerPoint%20slide%2C%20show%2010%20to%2015%20systems%20that%20fit%20together%20simply%20and%20together%20represent%20the%20only%20systems%20needed%20to%20get%20all%20the%20way%20from%20selling%20a%20ticket%20to%20delivering%20the%20passenger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20founder%20Ken%20Griffin's%20market%20maker%20is%20revamping%20its%20core%20trading%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20is%20the%20collection%20of%20systems%20and%20technologies%20that%20executes%20one%20in%20every%20four%20equity%20trades%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%20or%20two%2C%20Maurone%20and%20Josh%20Woods%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-securities-ceo-peng-zhao-olympics-career-advice-interns-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitadel%20Securities%3C%2Fa%3E'%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20have%20been%20strategizing%20to%20consolidate%20redundancies%2C%20mitigate%20operational%20complexities%2C%20and%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20trading%20and%20entering%20new%20businesses.%20They're%20looking%20across%20the%20entire%20lifecycle%20of%20a%20trade%20as%20a%20blueprint%20for%20the%20rebuild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%20in%202002%2C%20Citadel%20Securities%20has%20used%20predictive%20analytics%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-securities-data-ken-griffin-markets-assets-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20technology%20to%20allow%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20to%20trade%20assets%20by%20providing%20market%20liquidity.%20It%20uses%20algorithms%20to%20capture%20profit%20from%20small%20differences%20in%20prices.%20In%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20market%20maker%20has%20expanded%20in%20the%20types%20of%20clients%20it%20works%20with%2C%20the%20products%20it%20trades%2C%20and%20the%20exchanges%20where%20it%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20prepare%20the%20firm%20for%20what%20lies%20ahead%20while%20delivering%20more%20resiliency%20and%20capabilities%20to%20clients%20today%2C%20Woods%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20way%20to%2C%20over%20time%2C%20keep%20your%20agility.%20I%20almost%20look%20at%20it%20as%20the%20stretching%20of%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Woods%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20do%20these%20things%2C%20your%20technology%20stack%20eventually%20gets%20more%20rigid%20than%20you'd%20like%2C%20and%20then%20when%20you%20need%20to%20stretch%2C%20you're%20unable%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c49a2ec2-8ae0-4677-96cd-94e7f2168232%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20Citadel%20Securities'%20trading%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Citadel%20Securities%20pushed%20into%20credit%20trading%2C%20expanded%20its%20rates%20franchise%2C%20and%20introduced%20an%20institutional%20options%20offering.%20It%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-wall-street-executives-rising-stars-investing-trading-2024%23gidan-dan-35-citadel-securities-13%5C%22%20target