ifferences%20in%20trading%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20from%20systematic%20to%20high-touch%20%E2%80%94%20will%20require%20Citadel%20Securities%20to%20rethink%20those%20underlying%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20several%20progressive%20changes%20to%20its%20tech%20stack%2C%20Maurone%20said%20he%20hopes%20that%20in%202025%2C%20the%20firm%20will%20be%20entirely%20trading%20in%20a%20system%20that%20reflects%20its%20goal%20to%20reduce%20operational%20complexity%20and%20redundancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20it%20requires%20reorienting%20how%20we%20look%20at%20the%20problem.%20Before%2C%20you%20couldn't%20really%20see%20the%20pattern%20because%20you're%20only%20looking%20at%20one%20little%20slice%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20now%20that%20you%20see%20it%20across%20all%20these%20different%20domains%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20there's%20more%20we%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Woods%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a4344c0-c7a7-4dfd-9e99-50d4262adc9b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20product%20managers%20are%20bridging%20business%20and%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20firms%20have%20long%20turned%20to%20consulting%20agencies%2C%20like%20McKinsey%20or%20Deloitte%2C%20to%20shepherd%20tech%20execs%20and%20other%20C-suites%20through%20a%20transformative%20process%20such%20as%20this.%20Instead%2C%20Citadel%20Securities%20has%20turned%20to%20an%20internal%20group%20of%20product%20managers%20and%20COOs%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20whom%20spent%20years%20working%20at%20consulting%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20to%20oversee%20the%20vision%20and%20execution%20of%20its%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20out%20this%20internal%20muscle%2C%20Maurone%20said%2C%20has%20filled%20a%20need%20that%20an%20external%20consultant%20never%20really%20could.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20live%20and%20breathe%20and%20own%20the%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Maurone%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20much%20of%20the%20software%20is%20created%20in-house.%20%