0Malik%20that%20the%20protest%20against%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20developed%20cracks%20when%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20close%20to%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20Vinesh%20began%20to%20fill%20her%20mind%20with%20%26quot%3Bgreed%26quot%3B.%20Sakshi%20also%20alleged%20that%20Vinesh%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia's%20decision%20to%20accept%20exemption%20from%20Asian%20Games%20trails%20also%20tarnished%20the%20image%20of%20the%20protests.%20However%2C%20Vinesh%20dismissed%20any%20such%20speculations%20and%20said%20that%20they%20fought%20for%20a%20good%20cause%20before%20adding%20that%20if%20speaking%20up%20for%20athletes%20is%20%26quot%3Bgreed%26quot%3B%2C%20then%20she%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20such%20%26quot%3Bgreed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20gave%20me%20anything%20in%20writing%2C%20nor%20can%20I%20assume%20someone's%20intentions.%20The%20good%20thing%20is%20that%20we%20fought%20for%20a%20good%20cause.%20If%20playing%20in%20the%20Olympics%20and%20winning%20a%20medal%20for%20our%20country%20is%20greed%2C%20then%20yes%2C%20I%20will%20carry%20that%20'greed'%20till%20my%20last%20breath.%20What%20exactly%20is%20greed%3F%20If%2C%20as%20an%20athlete%2C%20speaking%20up%20for%20fellow%20athletes%20and%20standing%20by%20my%20sisters%20is%20greed%2C%20then%20I%20consider%20it%20a%20good%20kind%20of%20greed.%20The%20desire%20to%20play%20for%20the%20country%20should%20always%20remain%2C%26quot%3B%20Phogat%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwill-carry-this-greed-till-death-vinesh-phogat-on-sakshi-maliks-charge-over-wrestlers-protest%2Farticleshow%2F114458964.cms%5C%22%3EANI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20prominent%20faces%20of%20the%20prolonged%20protest%2C%20made%20this%20statement%20in%20her%20recently-released%20book%20'Witness'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-olk-copy-source%3D%5C%22MessageBody%5C%22%3E%26quot%