0X%2C%20using%20automated%20bots.%20He%20has%20since%20expanded%20his%20accounts%20to%20Instagram%20and%20Threads%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-who-tracks-elon-musk-jet-launching-own-website-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elaunched%20his%20own%20database%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20monitoring%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accounts%20have%20caused%20controversy%20and%20upset%20some%20powerful%20people%2C%20including%20Musk%20and%20Swift.%20Both%20have%20threatened%20Sweeney%20with%20separate%20lawsuits%2C%20with%20Swift%20referring%20to%20the%20accounts%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2F02%2F06%2Ftaylor-swift-jet-tracking-legal-threat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bstalking%20and%20harassing%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20college%20student%20first%20made%20headlines%20in%202022%20after%20Musk%20offered%20him%20money%20to%20stop%20publicly%20sharing%20his%20flight%20information.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Sweeney%20was%20a%20freshman%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida%20in%20Orlando%2C%20studying%20information%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20previously%20told%20BI%20he%20tried%20negotiating%20a%20higher%20price%20tag%20but%20never%20heard%20back%20from%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20Sweeney's%20jet-tracking%20accounts%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-booted-elon-musk-jet-tracking-account-left-mark-zuckerberg-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esuspended%20by%20X.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Musk%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20social%20media%20company%20months%20earlier%2C%20called%20the%20accounts%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-booted-elon-musk-jet-tracking-account-left-mark-zuckerberg-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bphysical%20safety%20violation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20X%20has%20updated%20its%20policies%20to%20restrict%20users%20from%20sharing%20other%20people's%20live%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjet-tracking-accounts-suspended-threads-meta-jack-sweeney-mark-zuckerberg-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729598388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671787b4a0a0cc14f222e652%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjet-tracking-accounts-suspended-threads-meta-jack-sweeney-mark-zuckerberg-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20cited%20privacy%20policy%20violations%20and%20potential%20physical%20harm%20as%20reasons%20for%20suspending%20the%20accounts%20tracking%20private%20jets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjet-tracking-accounts-suspended-threads-meta-jack-sweeney-mark-zuckerberg-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Really%20putting%20Ukraine's%20Abrams%20and%20F-16s%20to%20work%20fighting%20Russia%20means%20most%20probably%20won't%20survive%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20kind%20of%20war%20this%20is%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20stand%20beside%20an%20F-16%20on%20a%20runway%20in%20front%20of%20trees%20and%20half%20under%20some%20material%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6710e3afa703186492837ae6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-16%20after%20it%20first%20arrived%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20August%202024.%3Cp%3EVitalii%20Nosach%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20of%20Ukraine's%20Western%20weapons%20won't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20if%20it%20really%20uses%20them%2C%20experts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWeapons%20like%20Abrams%20and%20F-16s%20have%20been%20given%20in%20small%20numbers%2C%20so%20Ukraine%20needs%20to%20take%20risks%20to%20maximize%20them%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20any%20of%20them%20survive%20the%20war%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20probably%20weren't%20used%20to%20their%20maximum%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20warfare%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brutal%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20conflict%20that%20is%20going%20to%20consume%20the%20Western%20tanks%20and%20fighter%20jets%20sent%20if%20Kyiv's%20forces%20really%20put%20them%20to%20work%20in%20battle%2C%20war%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20West%20shouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20none%20of%20them%20make%20it%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20intense%2C%20large-scale%2C%20protracted%20fight%2C%20and%20the%20Ukrainians%20need%20to%20make%20bold%2C%20high-risk%2C%20high-reward%20plays%2C%20they%20said.%20That%20doesn't%20preclude%20caution%2C%20but%20using%20them%20to%20their%20fullest%20risks%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20of%20the%20F-16s%20make%20it%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%2C%20they%20probably%20weren't%20used%20hard%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Bohnert%2C%20an%20air%20warfare%20expert%20at%20RAND%20Corporation%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hate%20saying%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we%20as%20the%20West%20have%20to%20realize%20every%20Abrams%20tank%20that%20was%20given%2C%20every%20F-16%2C%20if%20any%20of%20them%20make%20it%20through%20the%20war%2C%20they%20probably%20weren't%20used%20to%20their%20maximum%20extent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20Western%20partners%20sent%20fighters%20and%20tanks%20in%20small%20numbers%2C%20and%20those%20small%20numbers%20limit%20what%20Ukraine%20can%20do%20with%20the%20weapons.%20Maximizing%20potential%20means%20raising%20risks%2C%20and%20using%20them%20to%20their%20fullest%20is%20going%20to%20mean%20losses%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%20flying%20across%20gray%20skies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cdcf3d1aa2ac29ee348231%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221933%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20air%20force%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%20flies%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Alberque%2C%20a%20warfare%20expert%20at%20the%20Stimson%20Center%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Western%20weapons%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20maximization%20of%20potential%20means%20that%20a%20lot%2C%20if%20not%20all%20of%20them%2C%20may%20be%20destroyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20weapons%20are%20%26quot%3Bdestroyed%20doing%20things%20that%20Ukraine%20could%20not%20have%20done%20otherwise%20and%20inflicting%20massive%20losses%20on%20Russia%2C%20then%20it's%20entirely%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20giving%20them%20with%20the%20understanding%20that%20we're%20not%20getting%20them%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227dd047ab-a34b-4db4-8060-2629ab9a549c%5C%22%3ERisk%20is%20necessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlberque%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3Beverything%20that%20we%20give%20Ukraine%20we%20have%20to%20assume%20can%20and%20will%20be%20destroyed%20in%20combat%2C%20but%20at%20the%20very%20least%20must%20be%20used%20to%20absolute%20maximum%20potential.%20And%20that%20entails%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20anyone%20who%20doesn't%20understand%20that%20doesn't%20understand%20the%20concept%20of%20generosity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBohnert%20noted%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20do%20have%20to%20weigh%20the%20risk%20against%20%26quot%3Bthe%20propaganda%20that%20Russia%20will%20say%3A%20'Oh%2C%20we%20shot%20down%20F-16s.%20Oh%2C%20we%20blew%20up%20an%20Abrams%2C%20et%20cetera.'%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20this%20is%20winning%20a%20war%20and%20making%20sure%20Ukraine%20wins%20a%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soldier%20climbing%20down%20from%20the%20front%20of%20a%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tank.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6698104afb2b6bedb05808c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20on%20a%20US-provided%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tank%20at%20an%20undisclosed%20location.%3Cp%3E47th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20via%20Telegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20being%20put%20off%20by%20the%20potential%20for%20Russian%20celebration%2C%20Bohnert%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20in%20the%20West%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20accept%20that%20none%20of%20those%20F-16s%20might%20come%20home.%20The%20pilots%20hopefully%20come%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20World%20War%20II%2C%20most%20of%20the%20planes%20that%20we%20started%20with%20didn't%20end%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20forces%20have%20already%20lost%20some%20of%20their%20Abrams%20tanks%2C%20numerous%20Bradley%20fighting%20vehicles%2C%20a%20number%20of%20Leopard%20tanks%2C%20and%20at%20least%20one%20of%20its%20new%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%2C%20at%20times%20leading%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20value%20of%20the%20support%20being%20provided%2C%20but%20war%20analysts%20argue%20that%20isn't%20a%20reason%20for%20partners%20to%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Barros%2C%20a%20Russia%20expert%20and%20geospatial%20analyst%20at%20the%20Insitute%20at%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bpointing%20at%20some%20destroyed%20Ukrainian%20planes%20and%20lost%20pilots%20and%20then%20coming%20away%20with%20the%20conclusion%20like%20'Oh%2C%20shoot%2C%20we%20can't%20do%20this'%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20the%20wrong%20way%20to%20look%20at%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20approaching%20it%20like%20that%20would%20be%20like%20Americans%20looking%20at%20what%20was%20happening%20%26quot%3Bin%20World%20War%20II%20at%20the%20Battle%20of%20Britain%20and%20saying%3A%20'Oh%2C%20man%2C%20the%20Brits%20are%20losing%20a%20lot%20of%20Spitfires%2C%20why%20are%20we%20still%20sending%20the%20UK%20raw%20materials%20and%20weapons%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20a%20catastrophic%2C%20high-casualty%20fight%20that%20has%20claimed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20lives%2C%20eating%20through%20men%20and%20equipment%20like%20the%20European%20continent%20hasn't%20seen%20in%20decades%2C%20really%20not%20since%20WWII.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBohnert%20said%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20just%20sadly%20the%20nature%20of%20warfare%2C%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20come%20home.%20A%20lot%20of%20equipment%20never%20sees%20it%20through%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%20in%20recent%20decades%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20used%20to%20wars%20where%205%2C%2010%2C%2020%20people%20die%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20wars%20like%20Iraq%20or%20Afghanistan%2C%20wars%20that%2C%20while%20tragic%2C%20didn't%20come%20close%20to%20this%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20used%20to%20these%20very%20low-casualty%20wars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20that's%20atypical%20in%20the%20history%20of%20mankind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20contrast%20between%20the%20slow%2C%20horrifically%20bloody%2C%20grinding%20war%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20that%20has%20seen%20massive%20casualties%20and%20the%20recent%20wars%20the%20West%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20is%20one%20that%20many%20warfare%20experts%20have%20commented%20on%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine%20servicemen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661a690a3f923f7dab07b941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20servicemen%20fighting%20off%20Russian%20troops%20in%20Donetsk%20Oblast%3Cp%3EWolfgang%20Schwan%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20veteran%20who%20fought%20in%20Ukraine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-fighters-die-in-ukraine-assume-be-easy-us-veteran-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20are%20many%20Western%20fighters%20who%20come%20to%20Ukraine%20thinking%20it%20will%20be%20easy%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20they%20find%20that%20their%20training%20has%20not%20sufficiently%20prepared%20them%20for%20the%20intensity.%20Many%20have%20been%20killed%20as%20a%20result%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukraine%20war%20is%20a%20challenging%20fight%20where%20troops%20and%20equipment%20are%20consistently%20at%20risk%20because%20these%20assets%20are%20either%20shields%20or%20spears%2C%20either%20blunting%20a%20Russian%20attack%20or%20being%20used%20to%20break%20through%20Russian%20defenses%2C%20and%20that%20is%20going%20to%20mean%20losses%20if%20they're%20being%20put%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20lost%20its%20first%20F-16%20during%20an%20air-defense%20mission%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20cities%20from%20a%20massive%20Russian%20missile%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20Ukrainian%2C%20would%20you%20rather%20have%20lost%20an%20F-16%20or%20an%20orphanage%3F%20This%20is%20the%20way%20we%20have%20to%20start%20thinking.%20This%20is%20the%20way%20the%20West%20has%20to%20start%20thinking%20of%20aid%3A%20That%20it's%20to%20win.%20It's%20not%20for%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohnert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20undersides%20of%202%20F-16s%20are%20seen%20flying%20against%20a%20grey%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67065c5c3f2165d716df761e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221291%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20Air%20Force's%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlberque%20said%20that%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20risks%20are%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20ensure%20that%20you%20don't%20lose%20any%20F-16s%20if%20you%20don't%20fly%20any%20of%20them%20and%20you%20keep%20them%20in%20deep%20underground%20caves%2C%20but%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258b8e595-abdc-4fda-945b-e1f50bf41d2f%5C%22%3ENot%20the%20best%20stuff%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20only%20received%20a%20small%20number%20of%20F-16s%2C%20and%20so%20far%2C%20it%20has%20only%20received%20roughly%20a%20few%20dozen%20Abrams.%20With%20limited%20stockpiles%2C%20it%20has%2C%20at%20times%2C%20tried%20to%20play%20it%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlberque%20argued%20that%20Ukraine%20should%20consider%20taking%20more%20risks%20with%20them%2C%20because%20with%20so%20few%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20better%20use%20them%20hard%20because%20you%20can't%20hold%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBohnert%2C%20likewise%2C%20said%20the%20West%20should%20allow%20Ukraine%20to%20take%20more%20risks%20with%20its%20weapons.%20He%20said%20the%20West%2C%20for%20example%2C%20should%20not%20restrict%20how%20Ukraine%20uses%20its%20F-16s%2C%20weapons%20that%20were%20first%20made%20by%20General%20Dynamics%20before%20that%20later%20passed%20to%20Lockheed%20Martin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenmark%2C%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20giving%20Ukraine%20F-16s%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3