ne%20of%20the%20first%20being%20between%20Congress's%20Balasaheb%20Thorat%20and%20Mr%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20round%20of%20meeting%20has%20been%20held%20in%20the%20morning%20between%20the%20Sena%20UBT%20and%20the%20Congress.%20A%20second%20round%20is%20in%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20its%20conclusions%2C%20an%20announcement%20is%20likely%20within%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20said%20Congress's%20state%20chief%20Nana%20Patole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20had%20said%20that%20the%20MVA%20had%20reached%20a%20consensus%20on%20210%20out%20of%20288%20assembly%20seats%2C%20while%20Nana%20Patole%20claimed%20the%20figure%20was%2096.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20parties%20have%20been%20bargaining%20for%20days%20as%20Mr%20Patole%20held%20out%20for%20125%20seats%20while%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20pushing%20for%20100%20seats%20each%20for%20it%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%2088%20for%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20issue%20that%20has%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Congress%20grouse%20-%20%26quot%3BWhichever%20party%20is%20strong%20and%20meritorious%20will%20fight%20in%20the%20respective%20constituency%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20Congress%20is%20holding%20out%20for%20the%20eight%20seats%20in%20Vidarbha%20that%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20party%20wants.%20Senior%20Sena%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20has%20said%20while%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20the%20Congress%20having%20a%20strong%20base%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20also%20had%204-5%20MPs%20from%20there%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20also%20get%201%20or%202%20seats%2C%20then%20there%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20the%20288-member%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2020%2C%20and%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20N