vocation%2C%20Malhotra%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3B%20As%20far%20as%20her%20membership%20is%20concerned%20absolutely%20she%20(Jemimah)%20is%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20country.%20We%20wish%20her%20well%20and%20wish%20she%20brings%20more%20accolades%20to%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20issue%20about%20that.%20The%20membership%20was%20given%20to%20her...The%20privilege%20was%20misused%20by%20her%20father%20using%20her%20membership%20and%20booking%20the%20presidential%20hall.%20The%20booking%20was%20for%201.5%20years%2C%20our%20members%20were%20not%20getting%20the%20space...To%20misuse%20that%20privilege%20is%20an%20issue...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhvi%20Ashar%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%20Khar%20Gymkhana%20also%20opened%20up%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20motion%20came%20up%20for%20hearing%20and%20when%20it%20was%20explained%20to%20the%20members%2C%20our%20President%20was%20charing%20the%20meeting%20the%20house%20was%20really%20upset%20to%20hear%20all%20this.%20Spontaneously%20it%20happened%20that%20her%20membership%20should%20be%20cancelled...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gymkhana's%20decision%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20the%20institution's%20by-laws%20and%20maintaining%20fairness%20in%20the%20usage%20of%20its%20facilities.%20While%20Jemimah's%20contributions%20to%20Indian%20cricket%20are%20celebrated%2C%20the%20Gymkhana%20deemed%20it%20necessary%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20misuse%20of%20membership%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERodrigues%20has%20played%20so%20far%20three%20Tests%2C%20thirty%20ODIs%2C%20and%20104%20T20Is%20for%20India%2C%20and%20accumulated%203087%20runs%20and%20six%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729597680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fkoti0b2o_sc_625x300_22_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-star-jemimah-rodrigues-gymkhana-membership-revoked-over-fathers-reli