%20so%20he%20is%20excited%2C%20he's%20like%20'What%20are%20you%20gonna%20talk%20about%3F'%20When%20I%20go%20home%2C%20he%20might%20ask%20me.%20So%20we%20will%20talk%20about%20different%20things%20that%20I%20said...%20These%20conversations%20are%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20about%20her%20son%20Jeh%2C%20Ms%20Kapoor%20Khan%20said%20she%20would%20want%20him%20to%20grow%20up%20into%20someone%20who%20would%20always%20stand%20by%20the%20truth.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Jeh)%20has%20a%20brother%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20he%20does%20not%20have%20a%20(duty)%20to%20protect%20other%20girls%2C%20he%20will%20be%20somebody's%20father%2C%20husband%20someday%20so%20I%20hope%20he%20values%20what%20his%20mother%20has%20done%20for%20him%20because%20he%20sees%20his%20mother%20and%20father%20go%20to%20work.%20So%20he%20understands%20that%20it%20is%20important%20for%20women%20to%20be%20safe%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%20to%20feel%20happy.%20These%20are%20things%20that%20he%20is%20watching%20every%20day.%20I%20want%20him%20to%20grow%20up%20knowing%20and%20normalising%20that%20women%20are%20equal%20to%20men%20and%20they%20can%20also%20be%20frontrunners%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729595820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6ropfplo_kareena-kapoor-khan_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-world-summit-kareena-kapoor-khan-mothers-must-kareena-kapoor-to-ndtv-on-raising-men-better-6847345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sensitisation%20of%20boys%20on%20gender%20equality%20must%20begin%20at%20home%20and%20mothers%20must%20have%20this%20conversation%20with%20their%20sons%20even%20if%20it%20is%20uncomfortable%2C%20actor%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20said%20at%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fin