ss%20works%2C%20learning%20the%20marketing%2C%20being%20part%20of%20that%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelf-publishing%20has%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20recent%20years%3B%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-disrupt-publishing-industry-eras-tour-book-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%20is%20embracing%20the%20model%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20lets%20authors%20break%20into%20the%20industry%20without%20getting%20signed%20by%20a%20literary%20agent%20or%20publisher%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20barrier%20for%20many%20writers.%20Authors%20can%20also%20share%20their%20books%20with%20the%20world%20more%20quickly%20and%20keep%20more%20of%20the%20royalties%20they%20make%20on%20their%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20money%20authors%20make%20self-publishing%20their%20books%20varies%2C%20but%20some%20writers%20previously%20told%20BI%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-kindle-income-stream-how-writers-make-money-self-publishing-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20over%20%2410%2C000%20each%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20by%20self-publishing%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20appeal%20of%20self-publishing%20for%20many%20authors%2C%20working%20with%20an%20established%20publisher%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20one%20of%20the%20big%20five%20like%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20or%20HarperCollins%20%E2%80%94%20is%20still%20the%20goal%20for%20many%20writers.%20These%20publishers%20offer%20expert%20editorial%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20sales%20staff%2C%20allowing%20an%20author%20to%20just%20write%20instead%20of%20worrying%20about%20how%20to%20get%20their%20books%20into%20the%20right%20hands.%20They%20also%20offer%20a%20sense%20of%20prestige%20that's%20often%20lacking%20in%20the%20self-publishing%20space%20unless%20an%20author%20finds%20wide%20commercial%20success%2C%20as%20Huang%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20started%20by%20self-publishing%20her%20