20abortion's%20on%20the%20ballot%20in%20Arizona%20this%20year.%20In%20an%20era%20where%20college-educated%20voters%20have%20been%20bleeding%20out%20of%20the%20GOP%2C%20Schweikert%20is%20increasingly%20an%20outlier%2C%20and%20he%20knows%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArizona's%20first%20district%2C%20redrawn%20ahead%20of%20the%20last%20election%20cycle%2C%20is%20the%20fourth%20most%20educated%20in%20the%20country%20that's%20still%20held%20by%20a%20Republican.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20have%20won%20it%20by%201.5%20points%20in%202020.%20Almost%20every%20statewide%20Democratic%20candidate%2C%20including%20now-Gov.%20Katie%20Hobbs%20and%20Sen.%20Mark%20Kelly%2C%20handily%20carried%20the%20district%20in%202022.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Schweikert%20bested%20his%20Democratic%20opponent%2C%20Jevin%20Hodge%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresults-david-schweikert-jevin-hodge-arizona-1st-district-house-election-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroughly%203%2C200%20votes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20year.%20%26quot%3BWith%20more%20money%2C%20we%20win%20that%20seat.%20The%20data%20is%20exceedingly%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20Jon%20Sutton%2C%20an%20Arizona-based%20Democratic%20strategist%20who%20worked%20on%20Hodge's%20campaign%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%20it's%20so%20hot%2C%26quot%3B%20Schweikert%20tells%20me%20as%20we%20sit%20down%2C%20as%20if%20it's%20his%20fault.%20It's%20just%20over%20100%20degrees%20outside%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20cooler%20than%20it's%20been%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20but%20still%20unseasonably%20warm%20for%20mid-October.%20It's%20fine%2C%20I%20tell%20him.%20I've%20mostly%20stayed%20inside%20here%20anyway.%20%26quot%3BA%20little%20bit%20of%20sunblock%20goes%20a%20long%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20offers%2C%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20someone%20who's%20had%20things%20cut%20off%20his%20back.%26quot%3B%20I%20assume%20he's%20talking%20about%20melanoma.%20%26quot%3BActually%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20pausing%20for%20several%20seconds%20as%20his%20face%20lights%20up%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20what%20you're%20here%20about%2C%20but%20look%20up%20'melanoma%20vaccine.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpancreatic-cancer-new-vaccine-promising-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evaccines%20for%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20congressman's%20been%20trying%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20them.%20That%20gets%20him%20talking%20about%20the%20vaccine%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-valley-fever-deadly-fungal-infection-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EValley%20Fever%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20disease%20caused%20by%20a%20fungus%20that's%20common%20in%20the%20Phoenix%20area.%20The%20congressman%20is%2C%20in%20his%20own%20words%2C%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20those%20people%20whose%20brain%20is%20going%201%2C000%20miles%20a%20moment.%26quot%3B%20Suddenly%2C%20he's%20distracted.%20A%20digital%20ad%20attacking%20his%20Democratic%20opponent%2C%20former%20state%20Rep.%20Amish%20Shah%2C%20has%20interrupted%20the%20YouTube%20video%20displaying%20Quranic%20recitations%20on%20the%20wall-mounted%20flat-screen%20TV%20across%20the%20room.%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20the%20district%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20raising%20his%20eyebrows%20as%20his%20face%20breaks%20into%20a%20wide%20grin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchweikert%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20sweating%20his%20reelection.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20gonna%20be%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20Sure%2C%20Democrats%20keep%20making%20inroads%20with%20well-to-do%20voters%2C%20but%20the%20congressman%20points%20out%20that%20his%20district%20includes%20lots%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-paradise-valley-richest-city-arizona-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20wealthy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%26quot%3Bentrepreneurial%26quot%3B%20constituents%2C%20and%20they've%20generally%20remained%20Republican%20throughout%20the%20Trump%20era.%20Even%20if%20some%20of%20them%20are%20repelled%20by%20their%20party's%20descent%20into%20populism%20or%20election%20denial%2C%20Schweikert%20thinks%20they'll%20stick%20with%20him%20in%20order%20to%20safeguard%20their%20economic%20interests.%20After%20winning%20here%20seven%20times%20in%20a%20row%2C%20he%20feels%20he%20still%20has%20his%20finger%20on%20the%20pulse.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20district%20that's%20functionally%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Schweikert.%20%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20here%2C%20I%20look%20like%20it%2C%20my%20education%20is%20exactly%20like%20the%20district.%20If%20you%20were%20going%20to%20go%20out%20and%20say%2C%20'here's%20the%20candidate%2C'%20I'm%20sort%20of%20the%20central%20casting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20keep%20looking%20like%20his%20district%2C%20Schweikert%20%E2%80%94%20a%20one-time%20conservative%20rabble-rouser%20who%20rode%20his%20way%20into%20Congress%20during%20the%202010%20Tea%20Party%20wave%20%E2%80%94%20has%20had%20to%20make%20some%20changes.%20He%20left%20the%20right-wing%20House%20Freedom%20Caucus%2C%20a%20group%20he%20helped%20found%2C%20shortly%20after%20his%20near-loss%20in%202022%2C%20telling%20me%20that%20the%20caucus%20had%20%26quot%3Bmigrated%20away%20from%20being%20sort%20of%20that%20free%20market%20group%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20once%20were.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20conservative%2C%20not%20a%20populist%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20his%20delicate%20handling%20of%20Trump.%20Schweikert's%20obviously%20no%20super-fan.%20As%20the%202024%20GOP%20presidential%20primary%20field%20began%20to%20take%20shape%20last%20year%2C%20the%20congressman%20told%20me%20at%20the%20time%20that%20he%20was%20closely%20watching%20the%20moves%20of%20one%20of%20his%20good%20friends%2C%20Sen.%20Tim%20Scott%20of%20South%20Carolina.%20But%20now%20that%20Schweikert's%20sharing%20the%20ballot%20with%20Trump%2C%20he's%20not%20sweati