%20of%20rules%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20statutes.%20Each%20thread%20represents%20a%20different%20aspect%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20from%20the%20contracts%20we%20sign%20to%20the%20rights%20we%20possess.%20Understanding%20this%20complex%20tapestry%20can%20be%20daunting%2C%20but%20it%20is%20essential%20for%20navigating%20the%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20that%20life%20presents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20series%20aims%20to%20unravel%20the%20legal%20tapestry%2C%20providing%20clear%20and%20concise%20explanations%20of%20various%20laws%20and%20their%20practical%20implications.%20We%20will%20explore%20the%20different%20threads%20that%20make%20up%20this%20intricate%20fabric%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344779%2Fworld-consumers-rights-day-landmark-judgements-consumer-law-in-india-online-orders%2F%5C%22%3Econsumer%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20maternity%20laws%2C%20traffic%20regulations%20to%20employment%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20exploration%20will%20delve%20into%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%2C%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20legislation%20that%20safeguards%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349558%2Fchennai-sankari-sudhar-job-portal-for-new-mothers-women-with-career-break-overqualified-housewives%2F%5C%22%3Erights%20of%20working%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20provisions%20of%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaternity%20leave%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMothers%20can%20enjoy%20up%20to%2026%20weeks%20of%20paid%20leave.%20This%20allows%20new%20moms%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20care%20and%20nourishment%20of%20their%20newborns%20without%20compromising%20their%20financial%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBenefits%20for%20commissioning%20mothers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20commissioning%20mother%2C%20you%20are%20entitled%20to%2012%20weeks%20of%20paid%20leave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWork-from-home%20option%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENeed%20more%20work%20flexibility%3F%20Under%20the%20Maternity%20Benefits%20Act%2C%20your%20employer%20can%20allow%20you%20to%20work%20from%20home%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20after%20you%20have%20availed%20your%20maternity%20leave.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECr%C3%A8che%20facility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Companies%20with%2050%20or%20more%20employees%20must%20provide%20cr%C3%A8che%20facilities%20within%20a%20specified%20distance%2C%20helping%20working%20mothers%20balance%20familial%20responsibilities%20while%20staying%20active%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInformation%20about%20benefits%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20joining%20any%20organisation%2C%20you%20should%20definitely%20inquire%20about%20their%20maternity%20benefits.%20Employers%20are%20required%20to%20inform%20women%20about%20the%20benefits%20available%20under%20the%20Act%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20initial%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20does%20this%20law%20apply%20to%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20eligible%20if%20you%20are%20pregnant%20and%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20organised%20sector%20for%20at%20least%2080%20days%20of%20continuous%20service%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20woman%20who%20has%20legally%20adopted%20a%20child%20under%20three%20months%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20woman%20who%20used%20her%20egg%20to%20create%20an%20embryo%20planted%20in%20another%20woman.%20For%20such%20commissioning%20mothers%2C%20the%2012-week%20period%20of%20maternity%20benefit%20is%20calculated%20from%20the%20date%20the%20child%20is%20handed%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%202017%20amendment%2C%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%20has%20had%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20working%20women%20in%20India.%20Apart%20from%20bringing%20into%20the%20l