20NIT%20Kurukshetra%2C%20he%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20UPSC%20preparation%20after%20graduating%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20rural%20background%2C%20Karamveer%20was%20deeply%20affected%20by%20the%20disconnect%20he%20observed%20between%20government%20officials%20and%20the%20common%20public%20in%20his%20hometown.%20This%20ignited%20his%20desire%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20work%20towards%20creating%20a%20more%20harmonious%20relationship%20between%20authorities%20and%20the%20people%20they%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20aspiring%20to%20join%20the%20Army%2C%20he%20faced%20challenges%20during%20his%20attempts%2C%20eventually%20pivoting%20towards%20the%20UPSC%20path.%20But%20his%20journey%20towards%20UPSC%20success%20was%20fraught%20with%20setbacks%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fias-ips-officers-share-useful-tips-to-prepare-for-csat-qualifying-paper-of-the-upsc-exam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Civil%20Services%20Aptitude%20Test%20%3C%2Fa%3E(CSAT)%20component.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Exam%20(preliminary)%2C%20the%20CSAT%20tests%20the%20analytical%20skills%2C%20reasoning%20ability%2C%20and%20aptitude%20of%20aspirants.%20Candidates%20need%20to%20score%20only%2033%20percent%2C%20as%20this%20paper%20is%20qualifying%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20excelled%20in%20the%20General%20Studies%20paper%20of%20the%20prelims%2C%20but%20the%20CSAT%20exam%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20hurdle%20in%20his%20initial%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20familial%20pressures%2C%20uncertainties%2C%20and%20previous%20setbacks%2C%20Karamveer%20remained%20steadfast%20in%20his%20determination.%20His%20perseverance%20and%20dedicated%20preparation%20eventually%20paid%20off%20in%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%202023%2C%20when%20he%20not%20only%20cleared%20the%20prelims%20but%20also%20secured%20a%20rank%20of%20954%20in%20the%20IRMS%20(Indian%20Railway%20Management%20Service)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20IRMS%20officer%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20embraced%20challenges%2C%20learnt%20from%20setbacks%2C%20and%20stayed%20committed%20to%20his%20goals%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20achieve%20success%20in%20the%20prestigious%20UPSC%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karamveer's%20dedicated%20preparation%20eventually%20paid%20off%20in%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%202023%2C%20when%20he%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369599%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaramveer%E2%80%99s%20dedicated%20preparation%20eventually%20paid%20off%20in%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%202023%2C%20when%20he%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrategic%20planning%3A%20Key%20to%20Karmveer%E2%80%99s%20UPSC%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20turning%20points%20for%20Karamveer%20was%20his%20realisation%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20CSAT%20exam%20and%20the%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20mastering%20its%20intricacies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prelims%20comprise%20two%20sections%20of%20General%20Studies%20and%20CSAT.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20qualifying%20paper%20where%20about%2080%20questions%20are%20asked.%20To%20clear%20the%20exam%2C%20one%20needs%20approximately%2068%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20200%20marks.%20In%20my%20first%20attempt%2C%20although%20I%20scored%20well%20in%20General%20Studies%2C%20I%20failed%20in%20CSAT%20by%20just%20three%20marks.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20the%20gap%20increased%20to%20nine%20marks%20when%20I%20reappeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20middle-income%20background%2C%20Karamveer%20also%20faced%20immense%20pressure%20at%20home.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20our%20family%20was%20surviving%20on%20his%20monthly%20pension.%20There%20is%20immense%20uncertainty%20in%20this%20exam%2C%20and%20having%20failed%20twice%20added%20to%20the%20pressure.%20My%20family%20was%20confused%20about%20why%20I%20could%20not%20even%20clear%20the%20prelims.%20It%20was%20becoming%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20stay%20motivated%20given%20the%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karamveer%20suggests%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys%20to%20improve%20marks%20in%20CSAT.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaramveer%20suggests%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys%20to%20improve%20marks%20in%20CSAT.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSAT%20section%20continued%20to%20haunt%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20genuinely%20scared%20of%20CSAT.%20I%20needed%20to%20improve%20my%20strategy%20for%20this%20section%2C%20as%20I%20was%20performing%20well%20in%20General%20Studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20his%20mistakes%2C%20Karamveer%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20engineering%20background%2C%20I%20was%20overly%20confident%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360088%2Fupsc-cse-hindi-medium-aspirants-ifs-officer-vikas-singh-meena-shares-tips-study-material-current-affairs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20clear%20CSAT%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20focussing%20solely%20on%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning.%20I%20neglected%20the%20English%20comprehension%20section%20and%20even%20avoided%20questions%20that%20seemed%20doable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20aspirant%2C%20we%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20UPSC%20tests%20your%20abilities%20in%20every%20section.%20You%20cannot%20choose%20to%20opt-out%20of%20topics%20that%20you%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with.%20In%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20I%20set%20my%20ego%20aside%20and%20gave%20equal%20weight%20to%20all%20three%20sections.%20That%20is%20what%20UPSC%20expects%20%E2%80%94%20do%20