0Cases%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369214%2Fprasanna-gettu-helps-domestic-violence-survivors-rebuild-lives-suggests-ways-to-end-crime-abuse-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomestic%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20and%20around%20the%20world%20spiked%20tremendously.%20In%20response%2C%20Indu%20felt%20that%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20safe%20spaces%20where%20women%20can%20rest%20and%20just%20be.%20This%20gave%20birth%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20safe%20space%20called%20%E2%80%98Namma%20Katte%E2%80%99%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENamma%20Katte%3A%20Where%20women%20can%20just%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20memory%20of%20women%20resting%20in%20public%20spaces.%20I%20would%20see%20men%20sit%20and%20have%20a%20smoke%20or%20just%20get%20together%20and%20chill%20outside.%20But%20I%20never%20see%20women%20do%20that%20in%20public%20spaces%20like%20under%20a%20tree%20or%20near%20the%20radio%20station.%20It%20was%20always%20indoors%20for%20them.%20This%20form%20of%20public%20existence%20%5Bin%20open%20spaces%5D%20was%20not%20there%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20that.%20So%2C%20Namma%20Katte%20was%20an%20open%20public%20space%20we%20created%20so%20that%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20children%20growing%20up%20could%20see%20women%20resting%20in%20public%20spaces%20as%20a%20common%20occurrence%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Indu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6VjvcTSFrx%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6VjvcTSFrx%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20